OL,3,CThree ambulance workers dismissed for
OL,4,Cunsafe driving
OL,6,FSouth East Coast Ambulance Service
OL,7,F(SECAmb) has dismissed three staff
OL,8,Fmembers following two separate
OL,9,Fincidents last year involving unsafe
OL,10,Fdriving in Trust vehicles.
OL,12,FThe incidents involved irresponsible
OL,13,Fdriving on a motorway and two staff
OL,14,Fmembers driving unsafely while
OL,15,Freturning to base.
OL,17,FSECAmb said the staff were dismissed
OL,18,Ffollowing thorough investigations in
OL,19,Fline with its clear standards and
OL,20,Fprocedures. One worker is appealing
OL,21,Fthe decision.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
