PN,38402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1781719875
OL,3,CThree ambulance workers dismissed for
OL,4,Cunsafe driving
OL,6,FBoth incidents were raised via the
OL,7,FTrust's Driving Standards Speak Up!
OL,8,Fportal, which was introduced following
OL,9,Fthe death of student paramedic, Alice
OL,10,FClark.
OL,12,FMs Clark, who worked for the South
OL,13,FEast Coast Ambulance Service, died on
OL,14,FJanuary 5th 2022 when the ambulance
OL,15,Fshe was travelling in crashed into a
OL,16,Fcement lorry on the A21 near
OL,17,FSevenoaks, Kent.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1781719875
OL,3,CThree ambulance workers dismissed for
OL,4,Cunsafe driving
OL,6,FThe paramedic driving the ambulance
OL,7,Fpleaded guilty to causing death by
OL,8,Fdangerous driving, and a coroner ruled
OL,9,Fthe ambulance service had failed to
OL,10,Fproperly investigate complaints about
OL,11,Fthe driver before the crash.
OL,13,FSECAmb says the Speak Up portal
OL,14,Fempowers staff to report concerns
OL,15,Fconfidently, ensuring that lessons are
OL,16,Flearned, concerns are acted upon and
OL,17,Fstaff feel supported to speak up in
OL,18,Fthe interests of safety.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
