FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1781719875
OL,3,CThree ambulance workers dismissed for
OL,4,Cunsafe driving
OL,6,FSouth East Coast Ambulance Service
OL,7,Fcovers a resident population of more
OL,8,Fthan 4.9 million across East and West
OL,9,FSussex, Brighton & Hove, Kent and
OL,10,FMedway, Surrey and parts of North East
OL,11,FHampshire. It employs more than 4,000
OL,12,Fstaff across 60 sites.
OL,14,FThe service said the safety of
OL,15,Fpatients, staff and the public remain
OL,16,Fits absolute priority and behaviour
OL,17,Fthat compromises this will not be
OL,18,Ftolerated.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
