OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1781719875
OL,3,CThree ambulance workers dismissed for
OL,4,Cunsafe driving
OL,6,FSince Alice's death, SECAmb said it
OL,7,Fhas strengthened its focus on driving
OL,8,Fstandards through enhanced training
OL,9,Fand Alice's legacy remains at the
OL,10,Fheart.
OL,12,FThis includes sharing learning through
OL,13,Finternal communications and the recent
OL,14,Flaunch of the 'Alice's Legacy: Driving
OL,15,FChange' podcast, where Alice's family
OL,16,Freflect on her life, the impact of
OL,17,Funsafe driving and the importance of
OL,18,Fembedding safer practices.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1781719875
OL,3,CThree ambulance workers dismissed for
OL,4,Cunsafe driving
OL,6,FDriving Standards Manager for SECAmb,
OL,7,FHuw Watts said: "The safety of our
OL,8,Fpatients, colleagues and the public is
OL,9,Fnon-negotiable. Where standards fall
OL,10,Fshort, we will take decisive action.
OL,12,F"Alice's death was a tragedy that
OL,13,Fcontinues to shape how we think and
OL,14,Fact. We are determined to ensure that
OL,15,Fher legacy drives real, lasting change
OL,16,Fby supporting our staff, strengthening
OL,17,Faccountability and making it clear
OL,18,Fthat speaking up and driving safely
OL,19,Fare essential to the care we provide
OL,20,Fevery day.
OL,26,@oD@QOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
