OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1781719875
OL,3,CThree ambulance workers dismissed for
OL,4,Cunsafe driving
OL,6,F"Our focus remains on supporting all
OL,7,Fstaff to uphold the highest standards
OL,8,Fof safe and professional driving at
OL,9,Fall times."
OL,11,FSECAmb said it continues to strengthen
OL,12,Fits focus on learning, transparency
OL,13,Fand prevention, ensuring strong
OL,14,Fsystems are in place not only to
OL,15,Frespond to concerns, but to stop
OL,16,Fincidents before they happen and
OL,17,Fsupport staff in delivering safe,
OL,18,Fprofessional care on every journey.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@KO]
